description.en:
Talented and talentless people.
Brought by the difference oftheir skills, is it a blessing or a curse?!

Misaki, who has loved video games since childhood, aspires to be part of the Gold Games company in the future and for this he enters to design school where he meets Kaname, a talented rising designer. Misaki sees Kaname as a rival whom he wants to defeat, because of this the frustration generated by his difference in abilities accumulates inside Misaki until he explodes with jealousy ... Is Kaname only making fun of Misaki or his true feelings do not reach him?
